OL,3,CThree more arrests made after murder
OL,4,Cof father-of-three
OL,6,FThree more people have been arrested
OL,7,Fafter a father-of-three was stabbed to
OL,8,Fdeath in Manchester.
OL,10,FAdrian Brown died in hospital after he
OL,11,Fwas attacked on Raby Street in Moss
OL,12,FSide at around 11pm on Friday 8 May.
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Police confirmed
OL,15,Fthat a 17-year-old and two 18-year-old
OL,16,Fmen have now been arrested on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
