OL,3,CThree more arrests made after murder
OL,4,Cof father-of-three
OL,6,FThe arrests bring the total number of
OL,7,Fpeople arrested to eight. Five
OL,8,Findividuals previously arrested in
OL,9,Fconnection with the incident have all
OL,10,Fbeen bailed pending further
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Alex Wilkinson
OL,14,Fsaid: "Adrian was at the West Indian
OL,15,FSports and Social Club in Moss Side on
OL,16,FFriday 8 May. Shortly after 11pm, he
OL,17,Fwas attacked and suffered fatal stab
OL,18,Fwounds.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
