CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778785872
OL,3,CThree more arrests made after murder
OL,4,Cof father-of-three
OL,6,F"There were around 200 people at the
OL,7,Fclub that night, and we believe some
OL,8,Fof those present may have information
OL,9,Fthat could help us piece together
OL,10,Fexactly what happened. This may
OL,11,Finclude eyewitness accounts, as well
OL,12,Fas photos or videos taken throughout
OL,13,Fthe evening.
OL,15,F"We understand that coming forward can
OL,16,Ffeel daunting, but any information, no
OL,17,Fmatter how small it may seem, could be
OL,18,Fvital to our investigation. Footage
OL,19,Fcan be uploaded anonymously via our
OL,20,Fdedicated Major Incident Public Portal.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
